-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-03/france-needs-adapted-volcker-bank-rule-perol-tells-huffington.html
France  should introduce an
“adapted” Volcker rule to ban banks from doing proprietary
trading, Groupe BPCE Chairman Francois Perol told the  Huffington
Post  website in an interview published in French.  To contact the reporter on this story:
